				<li>Money advance</li>
			</ul>
			All informations without (*) are not required.
			<br>
			<br>
However, Mail must be useful to sending the billing by mail. <br>
These informations are saved in RoomX database, into the table: guest.<br>
When check-in is done, you have this information: <i>Guest already exist, Check-in Done</i> . Like
During entering from <b>last name</b> field, you have a list of guests begining by the first characters entered.<br><br>
<br>
Additional Guest, is used in the case where you have a kid, or another person into the room.<br>
<b>Booking</b> check box is here to book a room if you are into check-in menu.<br>
<b>Booking Mode</b> display all rooms into the combo list to be able to book room. You are out of check-in mode. 
During the entering guest name, this field includes the auto-completion.<br>

